00:32:15,189 --> 00:32:18,794
[ Sniffling ]

565
00:32:20,128 --> 00:32:23,331
What Can I Make More Of,
Cielle?

566
00:32:25,132 --> 00:32:27,102
Abon, Don't.

567
00:32:25,132 --> 00:32:27,102
Ah!

568
00:32:28,936 --> 00:32:31,406
I Was In The Army.

569
00:32:31,439 --> 00:32:32,774
I Know About Integration.

570
00:32:32,806 --> 00:32:34,476
I Know All About It.
It Don't Work.

571
00:32:34,508 --> 00:32:36,478
It Don't Work!

572
00:32:36,510 --> 00:32:38,946
You Know, They Ain't--
They Ain't Treat Me
Like A Soldier.

573
00:32:38,979 --> 00:32:43,250
I Was A Colored Soldier.
A Nobody!

574
00:32:43,284 --> 00:32:46,321
It Was-- It Was Just Fine
With White Folk

575
00:32:46,353 --> 00:32:49,090
When I Was Willin' To Die
For This Country,

576
00:32:49,122 --> 00:32:50,958
But You Try To Give My Kid,

577
00:32:50,991 --> 00:32:54,295
My, My Beautiful Little
Daughter, What That Kid's Got,

578
00:32:54,327 --> 00:32:55,829
And They're All Up On My Back

579
