[ Whispers ]
Daddy Loves You.

600
00:34:30,258 --> 00:34:32,227
Give Me A Kiss.

601
00:34:35,128 --> 00:34:38,165
Go On.

602
00:34:35,128 --> 00:34:38,165
Let's Go, Ruby.

603
00:34:54,282 --> 00:34:56,885
[ Barbara ]
Miss Woodmere.
Miss Woodmere!

604
00:34:56,918 --> 00:34:59,053
As You Know,
She Has No Phys Ed,

