612
00:35:13,934 --> 00:35:15,903
That Is Exactly The Point.

613
00:35:15,936 --> 00:35:17,938
They've Given Us No Time
To Prepare,

614
00:35:17,972 --> 00:35:20,074
And I'm
Caught In The Middle.

