674
00:38:27,160 --> 00:38:29,430
You All Have A Nice Day.

675
00:38:32,733 --> 00:38:34,702
Good Afternoon.

676
00:38:36,804 --> 00:38:38,773
Um, I'll Tell You What.

677
00:38:38,805 --> 00:38:40,807
