690
00:39:36,896 --> 00:39:41,168
'Cept Worry About
How I'm Gonna Pay The Rent
And Take Care Of My Family.

691
00:39:41,202 --> 00:39:43,237
These Donations
Ain't Gonna Last Forever.

692
00:39:43,269 --> 00:39:44,771
I Understand How You Feel.

693
00:39:44,804 --> 00:39:46,873
I'm A Man With
A Family Myself.

694
00:39:46,907 --> 00:39:48,776
But... It's Just Temporary.

695
00:39:48,809 --> 00:39:50,444
In The Meantime,
We'll Make Sure

696
00:39:50,476 --> 00:39:51,811
Your Family's Needs Are Met.

697
00:39:51,845 --> 00:39:53,347
And Try To Remember

698
00:39:53,380 --> 00:39:57,352
What A Privilege It Is
For Ruby To Be Doing This.

699
00:39:59,220 --> 00:40:01,389
Really?

700
00:40:01,421 --> 00:40:03,456
Any Of Them Little
Colored Girls

701
00:40:03,490 --> 00:40:04,725
At That Other White School

702
00:40:04,758 --> 00:40:07,562
