Of Losin' Your Jobs?

706
00:40:18,671 --> 00:40:21,175
[ Boy ]
Uh-Oh. Daddy's Mad.

707
00:40:32,952 --> 00:40:35,789
I Don't Wanna Talk Right Now.
Go On Back Inside.

708
00:40:35,822 --> 00:40:37,791
Baby, I--

